---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Gamma PreQ - Acoustic Guitar Preamp, EQ & Boost"
  description="The Gamma PreQ is a DIY acoustic guitar preamp, EQ, and boost pedal designed by Ryan Schultz. Plenty of clean gain, flexible EQ, and a dedicated boost."
  ogImage="/images/pedals/gamma-preq2.jpeg"
  noindex={true}
>
  <link
    rel="stylesheet"
    href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/swiper@11/swiper-bundle.min.css"
  />

  <section class="bg-brand-dark text-white py-16 md:py-24">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 text-center">
      <h1 class="font-heading font-extrabold text-4xl md:text-5xl mb-3">Gamma PreQ</h1>
      <p class="text-gray-400 text-lg max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        Acoustic Guitar Preamp, EQ &amp; Boost
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-16 md:py-24">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6">
      <div class="md:flex gap-12 items-center">
        <div class="md:w-3/5 mb-8 md:mb-0">
          <div class="swiper rounded-xl shadow-lg w-full overflow-hidden">
            <div class="swiper-wrapper">
              <div class="swiper-slide">
                <img src="/images/pedals/gamma-preq2.jpeg" alt="Gamma PreQ" class="w-full h-auto" />
              </div>
              <div class="swiper-slide">
                <img src="/images/pedals/gamma-pcb-set.jpeg" alt="PCB Set" class="w-full h-auto" />
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="swiper-pagination"></div>
            <div class="swiper-button-prev"></div>
            <div class="swiper-button-next"></div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="md:w-2/5">
          <h2 class="font-heading font-bold text-2xl md:text-3xl mb-4">Designed for Acoustic Guitar</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-600 text-lg mb-4 leading-relaxed">
            The Gamma PreQ was designed specifically for acoustic guitar, although it will work for any acoustic instrument (but not bass). It has plenty of clean gain as a preamp, a plethora of EQ options, and a dedicated boost.
          </p>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4 leading-relaxed">
            It's quieter than most acoustic preamps and offers more EQ options. It's not as great as Grace Designs' ALiX (which is awesome), but it's close!
          </p>
          <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
            This is a <strong>DIY assembly</strong> you put together yourself. While this shouldn't be your first build, there's nothing particularly challenging about it other than its size (~150 total parts). Read the BOM and Build Notes carefully to comprehend the scope of this project.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  </BaseLayout>

<script is:inline src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/swiper@11/swiper-bundle.min.js"></script>

<script is:inline>
  // Use a slight delay to ensure the DOM is fully ready for the JS library
  window.addEventListener('load', function () {
    new Swiper('.swiper', {
      loop: true,
      pagination: {
        el: '.swiper-pagination',
        clickable: true,
      },
      navigation: {
        nextEl: '.swiper-button-next',
        prevEl: '.swiper-button-prev',
      },
    });
  });
</script>

<style>
  .swiper { width: 100%; height: auto; position: relative; }
  /* Make sure navigation arrows are visible over images */
  :root { 
    --swiper-navigation-size: 24px; 
    --swiper-theme-color: #ff5a1f; 
  }
  .swiper-button-next, .swiper-button-prev {
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
    padding: 30px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    transform: scale(0.6);
  }
</style>
